locality: Chute de l'Andromba. PK 33 route d'Antsirabe.
Faratsiho, rivière au sud ouest du village d'Ambohijafy.
Remnant forest along creek, along road to Col d'Itremo, W. of Ambatofinandrahana, ca. 5 km w of crossing over Imorona river, just W of village of Ambohimanatahotra.
Near P.K. 35 at stream-crossing N of Behenjy on road from Antananarivo to Antsirabe (R.N. 7).
District: Ambalavao Tsieniparihy, Commune:Ankaramena. Rivière Zomandao. Rivière à vitesse rapide. Echantillon préservé en alcool.
